Node.Description: Go to Accounts payable > Broker and royalties > Broker claims.
Click Broker report.
In the Broker field, enter or select a value.
In the list, select row 56.
In the list, click the link in the selected row.
Click Select.
In the From date field, enter a date.
In the Sales ID field, enter or select a value.
Click Select.
Select Yes in the Batch processing field.
In the Batch group field, enter or select a value.
In the list, select row 2.
In the list, click the link in the selected row.
Select Yes in the Critical Job field.
In the Monitoring category field, select an option.
In the Sales ID field, enter or select a value.
In the list, mark or unmark all rows.
Click Select.
Click OK.
Click Customer transactions.
In the Show field, select an option.
Click Settlement.
Click Settle transactions.
